  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>Designed for learners who want to work in Early Years, our course will develop your understanding of childcare and education in this sector.</p>
<p>Throughout the course, you will cover a range of units relating to childcare as well as take part in work experience in a variety of childcare settings.</p>
<p>On successful completion of the course, you could progress to Higher Education, or move into employment in a variety of supervised job roles in the statutory, voluntary or private sectors.</p>]]></mainContent>
