                {
                  "value": {
                    "dtgeContentTypeAlias": "widgetRTE",
                    "value": {
                      "name": "Rich Text Editor",
                      "text": "<h2>What could I do next?</h2>\n<p>Learners can progress into a variety of supervised job roles in the statutory, voluntary or private sectors. Roles including a practitioner in a day nursery, home-based childcare, or a pre-school worker.</p>\n<p>You could also progress to a Higher Education course USP College or work in areas such as: Teaching, Nursery Assistant and Nursery Supervisor.</p>\n<p>You could also attend university to study subjects like: Primary Education, Education Studies or a Foundation degree in Early Years.</p>\n<p> </p>",
